This paper deals with data management and natural language processing, which are both relevant to the database (cs.DB) and computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories. The use of deep learning models also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper's focus on ontology alignment and entity recognition could also place it in the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
